    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>概览</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一种变异病毒已在全球蔓延，将感染者转变为致命的僵尸和突变生物。人类最后的希望寄托在配备净化器的小型前哨站——这些装置释放净化烟雾以中和空气中的病毒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款极简俯视角动作即时战略游戏中，指挥一支幸存者小队。抵御一波波敌人的进攻。每个关卡都是为了保持净化器运行——并活下去的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/806ccc219d85a56e23808b1fa1f17577.poster.avif?t=1772280369\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/806ccc219d85a56e23808b1fa1f17577.webm?t=1772280369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/806ccc219d85a56e23808b1fa1f17577.mp4?t=1772280369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特关卡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都有不同的布局和挑战。净化器会吸引敌人——你必须保护它们以求生存和胜利。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>策略技能树</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁多种升级，塑造你的战术，提供全新玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/3190b0b58fed2c34f5de158f72c17066.poster.avif?t=1772280369\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/3190b0b58fed2c34f5de158f72c17066.webm?t=1772280369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/3190b0b58fed2c34f5de158f72c17066.mp4?t=1772280369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武器与物品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器和工具有限。合理利用它们，才能通关每个关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/054d6b379a692cb7e619aa35624eb4c1.poster.avif?t=1772280369\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/054d6b379a692cb7e619aa35624eb4c1.webm?t=1772280369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305010/extras/054d6b379a692cb7e619aa35624eb4c1.mp4?t=1772280369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
